              <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h5>Gentle Pressure</h5>
                  <p>Squeeze bulb gently - never forcefully. Water should flow gently along the ear canal wall, not directly at the eardrum.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="step-item">
                <div class="step-number">5</div>
                <div class="step-content">
                  <h5>Allow Drainage</h5>
